sect2.sect3:
Content language is no needed, chromo language is used instead.
		Current design - Conent language. Set content of conn point:

		    |  Cp : ConnPoint {
		    |      $ = "{ Provided:'Iface1' Required:'Iface2;}";
		    |  } 

		Embedded to native hier, content items to be created (Prop is the base Property agent):

		    |  Cp : ConnPoint {
		    |      Provided : Prop = 'Iface1'; Required : Prop = 'Iface2;
		    |  } 

		One more example of  - Debug property.
		    |  Agt : AStatec {
		    |      Debug : Prop {
		    |          Update = "yes";
		    |          LogLevel = "20";
		    |      }
		    |  }

